document_data.name: Windsummer Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Windsummer Street''' was one of the roads in the city of [[Urmlaspyr]] in [[Sembia]].
document_data.History: In the mid-14{{th}} century [[DR]], the adventuring [[wizard]] named [[Pendara|Pendara the Slim]] was one of the inhabitants of Windsummer Street in Urmlaspyr. In the {{YearlinkName|1352}}, she rode an untamed [[griffon]] and crashed it in front of her house.
